headline: GE Aerospace (GE): 3 Reasons We Love This Stock
summary: GE Aerospace currently trades at $327.27 and has been a dream stock for shareholders. It’s returned 251% since January 2021, tripling the S&P 500’s 83.7% gain. The company has also beaten the index over the past six months as its stock price is up 24.7% thanks to its solid quarterly results.
